程序包 io.github.moyusowo.neoartisanapi.api.item

接口 ArtisanItem.ComplexBuilder

封闭接口:
ArtisanItem
public static interface ArtisanItem.ComplexBuilder
Builder interface for complex custom items, allowing full customization of item stack data.

Usage example: 


 ItemStack itemStack = ItemStack.of(Material.DIAMOND_SWORD);
 itemStack.setData(DataComponentTypes.ITEM_NAME, Component.text("<red>Legendary Sword");
 ArtisanItem newItem = ArtisanItem.complexBuilder()
     .registryId(new NamespacedKey(plugin, "sword"))
     .itemStack(itemStack)
     .build();

    • itemStack

      @NotNull @NotNull ArtisanItem.ComplexBuilder itemStack(@NotNull @NotNull Supplier<ItemStack> itemStackSupplier)
      Provides the ItemStack Supplier for the custom item. Item count can be arbitrary.

      After providing Supplier, Supplier.get() will be called each time to dynamically generate ItemStack instances.

      参数:
      itemStackSupplier - the provider of the custom item's ItemStack (cannot be null)
      返回:
      current builder instance
      抛出:
      IllegalArgumentException - if rawMaterial is null
